F03%2F202726_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e65f7d85&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好咁快系統化咁去學文字<br />\n文字講話境同想像力<br />\n要自己去估</blockquote><br />\n散文重理詩講情，初接觸詩，覺得有啲詩句串埋一齊真係好難理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，好似有咩意象在內但無從捕捉咁，揣摩唔到原意，我覺得詩人係創作既過程中必定心猿意馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我都係學緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7658a8c7d354c4b88f81fb6d84555c0e6ed7abb","tid":484119,"uid":123907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T20:39:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>別忘了許願池也會吃金幣<br />\n<br />\n人生第一本新c</blockquote><br />\n你說，我不願看它一點點凋落。</blockquote><br />\n是的 為了避免結束"},{"pid":"c258329e07673ede28e37f0927147b9d2ae02961","tid":484119,"uid":12475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T22:57:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>別忘了許願池也會吃金幣<br />\n<br />\n人生第一本新c</blockquote><br />\n你說，我不願看它一點點凋落。</blockquote><br />\n是的 為了避免結束</blockquote><br />\n你避免了一切開始<br />\n<br />\n好gay"},{"pid":"115dbe01b36a1894473de515a00c977461852686","tid":484119,"uid":12475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T23:01:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>新手<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一次接觸新詩<br />\n買左呢本，淺談新詩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/03/202726_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F03%2F202726_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e65f7d85&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好咁快系統化咁去學文字<br />\n文字講話境同想像力<br />\n要自己去估</blockquote><br />\n散文重理詩講情，初接觸詩，覺得有啲詩句串埋一齊真係好難理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，好似有咩意象在內但無從捕捉咁，揣摩唔到原意，我覺得詩人係創作既過程中必定心猿意馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我都係學緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩呀<br />\n有時睇鍾意既詩人都睇到佢述句矛盾<br />\n其實要睇新詩要有相當既中文底<br />\n否則好難係句子搵到關連性<br />\n<br />\n始終新詩好多玩法<br />\n唔係一本通書既玩意<br />\n<br />\n有D巴打好強調搵詩眼去睇詩<br />\n但有D詩人根本無咁既概念<br />\n點搵個詩眼？<br />\n<br />\n依個係其中一個例子<br />\n講到尾都係要提升閱讀量<br />\n同大膽想像"},{"pid":"9caffb47379815f8efbbc1aa6072ba707bdec4a8","tid":484119,"uid":123907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T10:05:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>別忘了許願池也會吃金幣<br />\n<br />\n人生第一本新c</blockquote><br />\n你說，我不願看它一點點凋落。</blockquote><br />\n是的 為了避免結束</blockquote><br />\n你避免了一切開始<br />\n<br />\n好gay</blockquote><br />\n說好的c打"},{"pid":"84b25ef23b2aea7116368d6b4e994459394caaf9","tid":484119,"uid":113910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T10:23:43.000Z","msg":"夏宇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c691533b1434133c4363215ef2b131998f77836e","tid":484119,"uid":12475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T19:43:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>別忘了許願池也會吃金幣<br />\n<br />\n人生第一本新c</blockquote><br />\n你說，我不願看它一點點凋落。</blockquote><br />\n是的 為了避免結束</blockquote><br />\n你避免了一切開始<br />\n<br />\n好gay</blockquote><br />\n說好的c打</blockquote><br />\n我紅巴 慘"},{"pid":"7400700a1a1b0930266dfc000f91b5b1dc6f10b1","tid":484119,"uid":12475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T19:44:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>別忘了許願池也會吃金幣<br />\n<br />\n人生第一本新c</blockquote><br />\n你說，我不願看它一點點凋落。</blockquote><br />\n是的 為了避免結束</blockquote><br />\n你避免了一切開始<br />\n<br />\n好gay</blockquote><br />\n說好的c打</blockquote><br />\n我紅巴 慘</blockquote><br />\n期望文學少女倒不如去買六合彩<br />\n略有姿色既女仔都係鳩流流胸無墨水<br />\n就算有靚既文學少女都係鍾意靚仔多過文人"},{"pid":"bc2df51862086440fb4bd2cd16945fa3f25e9fba","tid":484119,"uid":12475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20